Trump has a "long history" of anti-Semitic behavior, says Biden's campaign in a harsh statement in response to the video. "Donald Trump is not playing. He is telling America exactly what he intends to do if he regains power: to rule as a dictator on a unified 'reich', said Biden-Harris spokesman James Singer.<br> "Speaking to parrot of the 'Mein Kampf' while warning of a bloodbath in case of defeat is the type of undesirable behavior that is obtained by a man who knows that democracy continues to refuse its extreme vision of chaos, division and violence."

